args: (I know I haven't come to look around in\na while, but I have a LOT of different types\nof vassals...)
(Some people are training in things I've\nnever heard of, and others are great at\nstuff I can't even begin to do.)
All righty then! I'm gonna watch these\nvassals until my eyes dry up and fall out!
Having taken a great interest in her vassals,\nYukimura decided to meet with every last one\nof them to learn their strengths and weaknesses.
One such person, a man named Jinpachi,\nespecially caught her eye...
Oh, there he is. HEY, JINPACHI!
Yes, I think so... I was just startled by\nsomeone calling out to me from behind.
I am so terribly sorry that you must\nsee me in such an unsightly state,\nLady Yukimura.
Woof. I knew you were easily startled,\nbut I didn't think it was THAT easy.\nI'm seriously sorry.
Please do not apologize, Lady Yukimura.\nIt's my own fault for being so fragile.
Well, I know there's a lot more to you than\nthe guy who gets startled all the time!
For example, I've heard about how\nfervently you studied military tactics.
Indeed. I thought such a talent might be of\nuse to the clan, so I studied many books\non the subject.
While I may not have talent in the ways\nof combat, I've always loved to read.
But I've been a coward since birth,\nand fear I will never be able to stand\nat your side on the battlefield.
I'm so ashamed. I would give anything\nto have just a little more courage...
Your body's not the only thing that can be\ntrained—we can also train your HEART!\nNow let's hop to it, Jinpachi!
EEEEK! I-it's so high up! There's no way\nI can possibly sit cross-legged on a\nprecipice so treacherous!
Okay, seems like that was a bust...\nRight then! On to your next training!
(Lady Yukimura told me to do this, but...)
The moment you think you can't breathe\nis when your training REALLY begins.\nJust hold out and surpass your limits!
I used this technique to push myself to the\nlimit and make my heart stronger!
(I'm definitely going to drown before my\nheart is able to get stronger...)
*gasp* *wheeze* I...I thought that was\nthe end for me...
I can't handle this kind of impossible—\nEr, I mean, this kind of HARSH training.
Lady Yukimura, please. Let's stop and...\nHmm? Where has she gone?
Sorry! Had to scoot for a hot sec.
Oh, but don't worry—I was ABSOLUTELY\npaying attention so I could help if anything\nhappened to you.
Lady Yukimura, I implore you!\nPlease let us put an end to these—
Ow. Ow ow ow ow ooooooow...
Yeah, I was fending off some fiends so you\ncould focus on your training and one of\n'em managed to swipe me.
I'm still learning how to fight and keep\ntrack of you at the same time, ya know?
Th-then you were hurt for my sake...?!
Oh, it's no prob. Seriously, do NOT worry\nabout me. Let's get back to your training!
Apologies, milady, but I simply cannot\nhandle such rigorous training...
Aw, you'll be fine! You've been honing your\nmind in the art of war all this time, right?
With that kind of guts and grit, you can\nDEFINITELY overcome this training.\nJust put your heart into it!
(That logic makes no sense...and yet she\nclearly believes in me!)
(I can feel her determination deep within\nmy very soul!)
(I must live up to her expectations!\nI cannot let her trust to go unfounded!)
Tch... Cat's outta the bag now.\nSurround 'em, boys!
We've come for the life of she who leads\nthe Monkey Wyrmclan!
Okay, who the hell are YOU people?
Don't worry, Jinpachi! I'll protect you!
Pathetic! Is that really all a Wyrmclan\nleader is capable of?
(Lady Yukimura is stronger than this...\nShe just can't handle her spear at the\nmoment because of her injury!)
(This is all my fault! She was injured\nbecause of me!)
(Dammit, Jinpachi! Stand and fight!\nThis is no time for cowardice!)
(I must prove worthy of her trust and show\nhow useful I can truly be!)
L-Lady Yukimura! I have an idea!
I am! I managed to overcome my limits\nso I could be of use to you!
Please hurry this way. I have a plan.
My life is in your hands!
You may rely on me always!
A plan? More like a fool's errand!\nGet 'em, boys! Get 'em good!
Gotcha right where we want ya,\nyou little rats. Now give up.
Actually, I believe it is you who is\nright where we want you.
They can't dodge now that they're lined up\non the steps, Lady Yukimura! You can take\nthem out in a single strike!
OH, I AM ALL OVER THAT! HAAAAAAH!
You call those chicken scratches attacks?\nI can't even feel 'em, ya foolish—

It's basic military tactics to take the high
ground, for the law of nature tells us that
water will always flow from higher places
to the lower.
As such, attacking from the high ground\nmake attacks that much more powerful!
Sweet puppy chow! It's like I was never\ninjured! Heck, I'm maybe even STRONGER!
So THIS is how you use military tactics!\nWith you by my side, there's no way I'll\never lose!
It is an honor to hear you say that,\nLady Yukimura.
And I swear to fight my fear and use my\nresourcefulness to serve you from now on!
